query: SELECT DISTINCT bf.eventoId, t.codigo FROM briefing_formando bf INNER JOIN formandos f ON bf.formandoId = f.id INNER JOIN turmas t ON f.turmaId = t.id WHERE t.codigo IN ('654', '974', '799') ORDER BY t.codigo;
